HELLO ! I'm an french kerbal engineer, with some craft to share with you : Jet (with missiles, obviously), shuttles, launcher, interplanetary vessels, probes, lander, rovers, drones, etc...

The most efficiency launcher series I have is the Keryouz serie (works since the 0.23.5 until 1.1.2, yeah) available on http://hangar.kerbalspaceprogram.fr/?usercraft=2608&page=5

you can download the rest on my creations in my hangar there : http://hangar.kerbalspaceprogram.fr/?usercraft=2608

Sorry, I'm not good in presentations... XD

Thanks !
You sir have either been playing KSP for a long time or you have some serious talent, either way you have some amazing craft.
